description:
As a user
  I want to check if my browser supports WebGL2
  So that I can use WebGL2-based applications

steps.name: I navigate to the WebGL2 test site
I should see if WebGL2 is supported
I should see the WebGL2 support message
I navigate to the WebGL Report site
I should see if WebGL2 is supported on the report
I should see detailed WebGL2 information
I should see the WebGL2 version
I should see the renderer information
I should see the vendor information

name: WebGL2 Compatibility Check
